### Customers Filter API Examples
### Base URL: https://localhost:7001/api/customers/filter

### 1. Get all customers (default sort by CreatedAt desc)
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 2. Filter by FullName (contains search)
GET {{baseUrl}}?fullName=John&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 3. Filter by Email (contains search)
GET {{baseUrl}}?email=@gmail.com&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 4. Filter by PhoneNumber (contains search)
GET {{baseUrl}}?phoneNumber=0123&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 5. Filter by Address (contains search)
GET {{baseUrl}}?address=Hanoi&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 6. Filter by Status (enum values: Active, Inactive, Suspended, Deleted)
GET {{baseUrl}}?status=Active&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 7. Filter by CustomerId (exact match)
GET {{baseUrl}}?customerId=12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 8. Multiple filters combined
GET {{baseUrl}}?fullName=John&status=Active&pageIndex=1&pageSize=5

### 9. Sort by FullName ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}?sortBy=FullName&sortDir=Asc&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 10. Sort by Email descending
GET {{baseUrl}}?sortBy=Email&sortDir=Desc&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 11. Sort by PhoneNumber ascending
GET {{baseUrl}}?sortBy=PhoneNumber&sortDir=Asc&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 12. Sort by Address descending
GET {{baseUrl}}?sortBy=Address&sortDir=Desc&pageIndex=1&pageSize=10

### 13. Complex filter with multiple criteria
GET {{baseUrl}}?fullName=John&email=@gmail.com&status=Active&sortBy=CreatedAt&sortDir=Desc&pageIndex=1&pageSize=5

### Available Sort Options:
### sortBy: FullName, Email, PhoneNumber, Address, CreatedAt, CustomerId
### sortDir: Asc, Desc
### Status values: Active, Inactive, Suspended, Deleted

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7001/api/customers/filter
